are now being fed on by the urban vector, _Aedes aegypti_.
Unless the vaccine virus has undergone an unprecedented increase in
virulence during the manufacturing process, the most likely explanation for
the tragic deaths from the vaccine is that the victims were
immunosuppressed, either as a result of an underlying infection such as
